    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Bevors to protect the chin and lower face, consisting of several lames articulated on sliding rivets, held in place by spring-operated catches or studs which, when released, allow the lames to fall open. They were commonly worn with open burgonets.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Gezichtsplaten om de kin en het onderste deel van het gezicht te beschermen, bestaande uit verscheidene harnasplaatjes die scharnieren om schuivende klinknagels die op hun plaats worden gehouden door veerpalletjes of verbindingsboutjes die, wanneer ze los worden gemaakt, de harnasplaatjes open laten vallen. Ze werden veel gebruikt  in combinatie met open helmen zonder vizier.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052462/Puype, Legermuseum Delft</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>保護下頦和臉部下半的護面甲，由滑動式鉚丁連接起來的金屬薄片組成，以彈簧機制的鉤扣或螺栓固定，鬆開時，金屬片會打開，這種裝置常見於開放式的帶面甲頭盔。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
